{"tid":1534633,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（大家要討論下）（比文宣睇）休息一陣好啦！我地仲有大把野要做","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T05:35:09.000Z","uid":21013,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c30a48565ef27d0c13cc947e859689881e545b7d","tid":1534633,"uid":21013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:54.000Z","msg":"手足好！我知大家都攰，不論勇武、和理非、文宣都已經好攰，咁耐以來真係好感激大家既付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。講明先，我唔係冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家入來傾下未來既活動。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本Post最主要先討論<span style=\"color: red;\">兩樣</span>野：<br />\n<br />\n1: 罷課既組織與行動<br />\n2: 未來日子既行動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Part 1:</span><br />\n<br />\n中學既罷課有好大既社會回響，但我發現各<span style=\"color: red;\">大院校</span>既罷課行動有<span style=\"color: red;\">欠「組織」</span>與<span style=\"color: red;\">「活動宣傳」</span>。雖然每個人都知要罷課，不過並唔係每個人都清楚「罷課既時候要做D咩」。<span style=\"color: blue;\">所以拜託下大專院校既手足搵一搵學生會幫幫手，係大Group到傾下大家應該做咩。如果唔係，罷課活動最後只會變成單純既「走堂」。</span>"},{"pid":"45ce46e5ee09013824bdddeecb6a8642743d4d0e","tid":1534633,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:20:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-a